# Auto detect text files and normalize line endings in git
# On Windows checkout: CRLF.  On Mac/Linux checkout: LF.  In repo: always LF.
* text=auto

# Explicitly mark as text (line endings handled by core.autocrlf)
*.js text
*.mjs text
*.html text
*.css text
*.json text
*.md text
*.txt text
*.svg text

# Binary files - never touch
*.wasm binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.zip binary
*.gz binary
*.tar binary
